{"type":"answer","id":239066,"parentType":"question","parentId":23472,"uid":8354,"contents":"如果像马来西亚那样，大学主要用英语教学，中小学校数理课程用英语（后一点可惜没有坚持下来），英语高考倒是的确可以取消。另：马来西亚高考（SPM）的数理类科目可以选择马来文试卷，也可以选择英文试卷，值得中国效仿。顺便贴一段马来语维基百科关于”自然数“的定义，粗体的词汇都是从英语直接引进的。<br>\n<br>\nDalam bidang<b>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ms.wikipedia.org/wiki/Matematik\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">matematik</a></b>,&nbsp;<b>nombor </b>asli&nbsp;boleh bermaksud satu unsur dalam <b>set</b> {<a href=\"https://ms.wikipedia.org/wiki/1_(nombor)\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">1</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ms.wikipedia.org/wiki/2_(nombor)\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">2</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ms.wikipedia.org/wiki/3_(nombor)\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">3</a>, ...} (iaitu<b>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ms.wikipedia.org/wiki/Integer\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">integer</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ms.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Positif&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">positif</a></b>) ataupun satu unsur dalam<b> set</b> {[url=https://ms.wikipedia.org/wiki/0_(nombor)]0[/url],&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ms.wikipedia.org/wiki/1_(nombor)\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">1</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ms.wikipedia.org/wiki/2_(nombor)\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">2</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ms.wikipedia.org/wiki/3_(nombor)\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">3</a>}, ...} (iaitu <b>integer</b>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ms.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Bukan-negatif&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bukan-<b>negatif</b></a>). <b>Set</b> pertama biasanya digunakan dalam&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ms.wikipedia.org/wiki/Teori_nombor\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><b>teori nombor</b></a>, manakala yang kedua lebih banyak digunakan dalam&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ms.wikipedia.org/wiki/Logik_matematik\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><b>logik matematik</b></a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ms.wikipedia.org/wiki/Teori_set\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><b>teori set</b></a>&nbsp;dan&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ms.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sains_komputer\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><b>sains komputer</b></a>.","date":"2020-04-13","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}